title: ‘KPop Demon Hunters,’ ‘Wicked,’ ‘Sinners’ and ‘F1’ Among Honorees at Hollywood Music in Media Awards
summary: “KPop Demon Hunters,” “Wicked,” “Sinners” and “F1” were among the honorees at the 16th Hollywood Music in Media Awards on Nov. 19 at The Avalon in Hollywood. “KPop Demon Hunters” took home the award for best song in an animated film for their hit “Golden.” The song was preformed by the group HUNTR/…
